<section id="problem" class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-label">核心问题</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">互联网的信任赤字</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
                当前互联网的身份模型是中心化的，导致数据孤岛、隐私泄露和单点故障。TSP提出了一种根本性的转变。
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comparison-grid">
            <div class="comparison-card" data-type="problem">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="card-icon">⚠️</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">传统中心化模型</h3>
                    <span class="card-badge card-badge-danger">代理式信任</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-diagram">
                    <div class="flow-diagram">
                        <div class="flow-item">
                            <div class="flow-icon">👤</div>
                            <div class="flow-label">用户</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-arrow flow-arrow-danger">
                            <svg width="24" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 60">
                                <line x1="12" y1="0" x2="12" y2="50" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <polygon points="12,60 7,50 17,50" fill="currentColor"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-item flow-item-danger">
                            <div class="flow-icon">🏢</div>
                            <div class="flow-label">中心化 IdP</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-arrow flow-arrow-danger">
                            <svg width="24" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 60">
                                <line x1="12" y1="0" x2="12" y2="50" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <polygon points="12,60 7,50 17,50" fill="currentColor"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-item">
                            <div class="flow-icon">🌐</div>
                            <div class="flow-label">应用/服务</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-content">
                    <ul class="feature-list feature-list-danger">
                        <li>信任由第三方IdP代理</li>
                        <li>用户数据集中存储</li>
                        <li>形成"蜜罐"和单点故障</li>
                        <li>隐私泄露风险高</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="comparison-card" data-type="solution">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="card-icon">✨</span>
                    <h3 class="card-title">TSP 去中心化模型</h3>
                    <span class="card-badge card-badge-success">点对点信任</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-diagram">
                    <div class="flow-diagram flow-horizontal">
                        <div class="flow-item">
                            <div class="flow-icon">👤</div>
                            <div class="flow-label">端点 A</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-arrow flow-arrow-success flow-arrow-bidirectional">
                            <svg width="100" height="24" viewBox="0 0 100 24">
                                <line x1="10" y1="12" x2="90" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <polygon points="0,12 10,7 10,17" fill="currentColor"/>
                                <polygon points="100,12 90,7 90,17" fill="currentColor"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-item">
                            <div class="flow-icon">🌐</div>
                            <div class="flow-label">端点 B</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-content">
                    <ul class="feature-list feature-list-success">
                        <li>直接点对点通信</li>
                        <li>用户完全控制身份</li>
                        <li>无中心化故障点</li>
                        <li>密码学保证安全</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    
    .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: var(--color-dark);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .section-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .comparison-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    
    .comparison-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        transition: all var(--animation-primary);
    }
    
    .comparison-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .comparison-card[data-type="problem"] {
        border-top: 4px solid #ef4444;
    }
    
    .comparison-card[data-type="solution"] {
        border-top: 4px solid #10b981;
    }
    
    .card-header {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fafafa 0%, #f5f5f5 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .card-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .card-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .card-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        border-radius: 1rem;
    }
    
    .card-badge-danger {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
        color: #ef4444;
    }
    
    .card-badge-success {
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        color: #10b981;
    }
    
    .card-diagram {
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        background: white;
    }
    
    .flow-diagram {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .flow-diagram.flow-horizontal {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .flow-item {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 0%, rgba(254, 249, 240, 0.9) 100%);
        border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        min-width: 140px;
        transition: all var(--animation-primary);
    }
    
    .flow-item:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    
    .flow-item-danger {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05);
        border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    }
    
    .flow-icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .flow-label {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    .flow-arrow {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .flow-arrow-danger {
        color: #ef4444;
    }
    
    .flow-arrow-success {
        color: #10b981;
    }
    
    .card-content {
        padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .feature-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }
    
    .feature-list li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .feature-list li::before {
        content: '✓';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .feature-list-danger li::before {
        content: '✗';
        color: #ef4444;
    }
    
    .feature-list-success li::before {
        color: #10b981;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .comparison-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        
        .flow-diagram.flow-horizontal {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
    }
</style>